# Domain 4: Prompt Engineering & Structured Output (20%)

## Explicit Criteria > Vague Instructions

"Flag comments where claimed behavior contradicts code" beats "check comments are accurate."

## JSON Schema via tool_use

Most reliable structured output. Eliminates syntax errors, not semantic errors. Use nullable fields to prevent fabrication.

## Validation-Retry Loops

Append specific errors on retry. Works for format issues. Does NOT work when info is absent from source.

## Batch Processing

Message Batches API: 50% savings, up to 24h. Good for overnight. Bad for blocking pre-merge.
